data.description: Imagine yourself in a captivating 4-bedroom home, where the convenience of having one of the two master suites downstairs awaits you. Picture waking up in the morning, just minutes away from the tranquil Oologah Lake, ready to embrace the day. Imagine your gatherings in the spacious living areas, sharing laughter and creating memories. Envision the warm, inviting atmosphere as you prepare meals in the well-appointed kitchen, complete with beautiful countertops throughout. The garage has been thoughtfully converted into a second master suite downstairs, adding to the home's versatility. Step outside and picture yourself enjoying the fresh air on your doorstep, knowing that adventure at the lake is just less than 2 miles away. This isn't just a house; it's a canvas for your dreams, where every room tells a story of comfort and joy. Plus, here's the exciting news: the home has been pre-inspected, QUALIFIES FOR USDA 100% FINANCING, and is on an ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.750%, making it even more accessible for potential buyers. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity. Call TODAY to schedule a showing and step into a life of comfort and tranquility.
